{
  "_comment": [
    "VEIMIA UGC Hub - Static + Serverless Hybrid Architecture",
    "",
    "Architecture overview:",
    "  - Static assets (HTML/CSS/JS/JSON) are served from /public/ via Vercel CDN",
    "  - Python serverless functions handle API logic (/api/*)",
    "  - Admin API writes JSON config files directly to /public/config/",
    "  - Campaign Page reads config from /config/campaigns/{id}.json (static)",
    "  - Changes propagate immediately on next page load (no build/redeploy needed)",
    "",
    "Config propagation flow:",
    "  1. Admin Panel -> POST/PUT /api/admin/* (serverless function)",
    "  2. Serverless function writes JSON to /public/config/ (filesystem)",
    "  3. Campaign Page fetches /config/campaigns/{id}.json (static file via CDN)",
    "  4. Changes reflect on next page load (< 30 seconds with CDN cache)",
    "",
    "Route priority (first match wins):",
    "  1. /api/* -> Python serverless functions",
    "  2. /config/* -> Static JSON config files (campaigns, products)",
    "  3. /admin/* -> Admin Panel static assets",
    "  4. /* -> Campaign Page static assets (catch-all)"
  ],
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "api/**/*.py",
      "use": "@vercel/python",
      "config": {
        "runtime": "python3.12",
        "maxDuration": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "src": "public/**",
      "use": "@vercel/static"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/api/(.*)",
      "dest": "/api/$1"
    },
    {
      "src": "/config/(.*)",
      "dest": "/public/config/$1",
      "headers": {
        "Cache-Control": "public, max-age=10, s-maxage=10, stale-while-revalidate=20"
      }
    },
    {
      "src": "/admin/(.*)",
      "dest": "/public/admin/$1"
    },
    {
      "src": "/uploads/(.*)",
      "dest": "/public/uploads/$1"
    },
    {
      "src": "/(.*)",
      "dest": "/public/$1"
    }
  ],
  "headers": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "X-Content-Type-Options",
          "value": "nosniff"
        },
        {
          "key": "X-Frame-Options",
          "value": "DENY"
        },
        {
          "key": "Strict-Transport-Security",
          "value": "max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/config/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Cache-Control",
          "value": "public, max-age=10, s-maxage=10, stale-while-revalidate=20"
        },
        {
          "key": "Content-Type",
          "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "source": "/api/(.*)",
      "headers": [
        {
          "key": "Access-Control-Allow-Origin",
          "value": "*"
        },
        {
          "key": "Access-Control-Allow-Methods",
          "value": "GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS"
        },
        {
          "key": "Access-Control-Allow-Headers",
          "value": "Content-Type"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
